# Yalak, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Yalak (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Akhtynsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. The population was 586 as of 2012.
Geography
Yalak is located 21&nbsp;km northwest of Akhty (the district's administrative centre) by road. Khryug is the nearest rural locality.
